{"word":"ἐρεείνω","slug":"ἐρεείνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐρεείνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>like <a href='S:ἔρομαι'><el>ἔρομαι</el></a>\n<p/><i>to ask</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to ask of</i> one, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to ask</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> dupl. <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <el>ἐρ. τινά τι</el> <i>to ask</i> one a thing, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>:—so in <a href='S:medium, middle voice'><a href='S:medium, middle voice'>Med.</a></a> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/>"}]}